

+ =Matthew 5:28= :: You have heard that it was said, “Do not commit adultery.” But I say to you that anyone who looks at a woman with lust has already committed adultery with her in his heart.

+ =1 John 2:15-17= :: But if anyone loves the Lord, he is a faithful witness, and this is how God’s love toward us was revealed: God sent his only Son into the world
